name: In—sight
description:
✦ 3rd/final Artwork for Obscure Delirium Series ✦

Obscure Delirium is a series made to capture the period in which one loses awareness of oneself and one's surroundings ✾

"In—sight'
Dalam penglihatan, dalam pemahaman

Searching endlessly
Fall off to the edge 
The smoke is too thick
Covering your sight
Sucking up a lemon 
Day by day
While everything you looking for is right in front of you
